---
title: Chicken in Creamy Peanut Sauce							 with coriander and rice
description: This peanut chicken dish is super quick to put together. Easy creaminess comes from the peanut butter while the accompanying fresh tomato, cucumber and onion salsa cuts through the richness for a balanced and tasty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230112_R12_W10_IE_IEQCLC13684-2_Main_high-bdfaa1ef.jpg
